Package GridPkg

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Grid
    Description: Grid is a mapping of a 2D surface in a cartesian plane; composed of square cells
    GridFileLoader
    Description: Takes data from a ".txt" file (specific format) and returns the contained integers as coordinates
    PreviewGrid
    Description: Paints a preview of a select Grid (and its cells) to the screen
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GridCell
    Description: Enum for each possible state of an individual cell of a Grid (Empty, Obstacle, Icon1:Yoda, Icon2:DarthVader, Color1:Green, Color2:Red)
